dat_set_data.pro


Routines

top source dat_set_data

NV/SYS

dat_set_data, dd, _data, silent=silent, update=update, noevent=noevent, abscissa=abscissa

Replaces the data array associated with a data descriptor.

Parameters

dd in

Data descriptor.

_data in

New data array.

Keywords

silent in

If set, messages are suppressed.

update in

Update mode flag. If not given, it will be taken from dd.

noevent
abscissa in

If set, the given array is taken as the abscissa.
